[common]
desc="<p>AngeMedia connects multiple image and video generation providers through one gateway on your NAS. Use Web Studio to generate media and manage jobs and results, or call the gateway from AI agents, automation scripts, and third-party tools through an OpenAI-compatible API or Gateway API Key. AngeMedia does not run local models; it handles Provider integration, job queues, result storage, and unified management.</p><p>Provider availability, quotas, rate limits, and billing depend on each service. No local GPU is required.</p><p><a href="https://www.777196.xyz/posts/ai-agent-image-proxy-gateway-prompt-routing" target="_blank">Read the Provider API key and setup guide</a></p>"
changelog="v0.2.1: Provides Web Studio, image and video generation, job queues, Provider management, Gateway API Keys, Prompt Copilot, and assistant skills. Requires Python 3.12 and Redis runtime packages. Python dependencies are supplied by the bundled offline wheelhouse. Does not run local models or require GPU access."

